<li>Assess autoscaling feasibility for SpeakUp and OneMeeting to handle traffic spikes</li>
<li>Identify and implement monitoring for critical third-party dependencies (joliet.granicus.com, etc.)</li>
<li>Update CR runbooks to include post-change validation steps (SQL listener IP verification, etc.)</li>
